{"tid":711391,"cid":20,"subCid":0,"title":"港珠澳大橋澳門口岸泊車轉乘計劃","createTime":"2018-06-21T13:19:08.000Z","updateTime":"2018-06-22T11:58:19.000Z","uid":33868,"like":7,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":13,"replies":[{"pid":"119af0ed2708ef6df445e57426a3ebdc6739b6ea","tid":711391,"uid":33868,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-06-21T13:19:08.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"http://www.td.gov.hk/tc/public_services/licences_and_permits/hzmb_macao_port_parknride/index.html\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fwww.td.gov.hk%2Ftc%2Fpublic_services%2Flicences_and_permits%2Fhzmb_macao_port_parknride%2Findex.html&d=whoAJaSLdZX72J61Z%2FbMTYzu7PIJYhBZqlGrkalTKs4%3D&h=bf69bef0\" target=\"_blank\">http://www.td.gov.hk/tc/public_services/licences_and_permits/hzmb_macao_port_parknride/index.html</a><br />\n<br />\n笑死人咩，<br />\n香港車主想開架車去澳門泊口岸停車場再過關入澳門、珠海，<br />\n唔計申請手續，首先要比：<br />\n<br />\n1. 每年香港禁區證540<br />\n2. 要買埋澳門同中國燕梳<br />\n3. 來回橋費（之前吹風大約120蚊人仔單程）<br />\n4. 澳門口岸停車場錢（暫時吹風係15蚊一粒鐘）<br />\n5. 油錢 <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n你唔收我1、2我都考慮吓得閒行吓，<br />\n仲要收我1、2 <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"2f6fd475184d92351070ffc7a61bddc5b867637e","tid":711391,"uid":65470,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-06-21T13:25:03.000Z","msg":"坐船算<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c6d7fe31063b6dddc79633f9b0e1b1dcffc8fbc7","tid":711391,"uid":51105,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2018-06-21T13:47:55.000Z","msg":"俾有錢人用，你估俾窮撚用？"},{"pid":"e309e3a72ee9a1b1bf619850be2a43aabcb434ab","tid":711391,"uid":79410,"like":7,"di